summary: This mod add a simple garden ahead breezehome with fences, flowers, a barrel, a tree and so on... (just take a look at the pictures)
descriptionHtml:
easier to install with NMM or simply extract breezhomeexterior.zip into your Skyrim/Data folder

This mod is not very useful, but during my rest times in skyrim i think to myself many times \\\\\\\"it would be pretty cool to have a small garden in there \\\\\\\' So I made this mod ;-)
author: R fama
